{"tid":2352944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際，或者流亡的人，最大的優勢，是國安法威脅不到他們","createTime":"2021-01-04T11:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T11:05:01.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"344cc1ab5fe6740723d777e4d8e5c94a49f72206","tid":2352944,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158824287152357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158824287152357&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZySHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=64ed2470\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158824287152357</a><br />\n<br />\n國際，或者流亡的人，最大的優勢，是國安法威脅不到他們，他們會以及可以說國安法所禁止的言論與事。換句話說，如果新的更激進政治主張有市場的話，國安法的存在保障了他們的專利。反之，他們的主張與本地民主派越近，就越沒有優勢，因為他們離香港太遠，而且會越來越遠。"},{"pid":"5c613a58b9df6c6f4e1ff9ad5e365770baf1e865","tid":2352944,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgXQwhR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgXQwhR.png&h=37c870d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLunch哥表示白卡先無敵"}]}